    "description": "You're the pharaoh, your goal is to defend yourself against the alien invasion. <br>They may have built the pyramids, that was a long time ago, they are yours now!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR DEFENSES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/1b781e5e9719fcc8c1e2f076b115a7c8.poster.avif?t=1696916947\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/1b781e5e9719fcc8c1e2f076b115a7c8.webm?t=1696916947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/1b781e5e9719fcc8c1e2f076b115a7c8.mp4?t=1696916947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Various towers and temples are available to help you defeat the alien invaders.<br>Each game you will acquire different buildings and have a different strategy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RELOAD YOUR BUILDINGS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/d9c872b2e9f819436ab7626be9330d21.poster.avif?t=1696916947\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/d9c872b2e9f819436ab7626be9330d21.webm?t=1696916947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/d9c872b2e9f819436ab7626be9330d21.mp4?t=1696916947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Tower defense games often suffer from being passive on the player's end, constructing the tower and just watching the waves crash onto them. <br><br>In Drafting Towers, the towers have limited ammo so keep an eye on that and make sure to reload at the right time<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DRAFT CARDS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/68bed3f8f70f79c22c139bc0f3e98a5d.poster.avif?t=1696916947\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/68bed3f8f70f79c22c139bc0f3e98a5d.webm?t=1696916947\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780950/extras/68bed3f8f70f79c22c139bc0f3e98a5d.mp4?t=1696916947\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Every once in a while, you will be able to draft a new card. The choice is different each game, adapt your strategy and don't let any invader in.<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100 cards<br></li><li> 25 buildings<br></li><li>20 difficulties to climb<br></li><li>Hundreds hours of gameplay</li></ul>",
